# 🧠 Today's Core Understanding

### Recursion

* Function calls itself
* Must have base case
* Solves smaller version of same problem

### Function Call Stack

* Stores active function calls
* Uses stack memory
* Follows LIFO

### Stack Overflow

* Too many recursive calls
* Usually caused by missing base case

